nodes.text: A female medic worked on the planet Kijimi. After deserting the Spice Runners of Kijimi during the Kijimi summit, an injured Poe Dameron was directed to the residence of the thief Von Tante by the smuggler Tarand Crowe. Tante called in a favor with the medic, getting her to help heal Dameron, who barely remembered the medic due to the delirium caused by his injuries.
